      • execute

        default IPacket execute(net.minecraftforge.fml.relauncher.Side side,
                        PacketContext ctx)
        A universal executor method for this packet.
        Parameters:
        side - The side that this packet was accepted on.
        ctx - The context that this packet holds. On server, contains sender as an EntityPlayerMP
        Returns:
        Reply packet, or null, if none.
